{"tid":418102,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"男童守龍門遭踢傷索償12萬 官判敗訴","createTime":"2017-09-29T09:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T13:04:41.000Z","uid":54373,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"1352f9001b4526eafab85cbbcb68a6be673de367","tid":418102,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506674781_0d08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506674781_0d08.jpg&h=2e6db5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2013年8歲的男童在葵芳工廈內踢室內足球時，聲稱在從未受訓下被教練指派任守門員，結果在一次撲波後遭衝前的另一球員踢中右眼。男童母親代表兒子控告兩教練及流浪足球會，索償12萬元。案件經審訊後原告今被判敗訴，須負責被告的訟費。<br />\n<br />\n原告男童李東諺，由母親<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獌</span>月玲</span>入稟，控告香港流浪足球會教練羅國豪、謝志明及香港流浪足球會有限公司。被告羅國豪於審訊時指，當日實非足球訓練，只是小朋友間的聯誼活動。<br />\n<br />\n法官在判詞中指出，足球是一項正常、大眾化及健康的體育運動，並不特殊，而守門員無論是大人或者小朋友都不會如原告人所言戴頭盔或者眼罩。再者，當日每位小朋友均由家長陪同到場，家長有責任照顧小朋友，儘管首被告邀請眾人到場玩樂，都不代表他須負責照顧在場每位小朋友的安全。"},{"pid":"6a495451fdef6480eeadce6605e0bd3aed4d93bd","tid":418102,"uid":32810,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:29:22.000Z","msg":"又係獌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9b95d334b99568e7a8007de0b451ef45843834","tid":418102,"uid":7940,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"支那蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84eb110733756ed71e3aeaa13391de46da43c287","tid":418102,"uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/173047_28e940edbcd1e81f5699a326ddd7f708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F173047_28e940edbcd1e81f5699a326ddd7f708.jpg&h=25c6e183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"293865aeea22f1b174a22a3372db2babdf412ab3","tid":418102,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係獌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"baa04f6b8005bb9bdf3b5fa6262f77ce84bd8612","tid":418102,"uid":148890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"抵能死。賠死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d841b8510470e3da476553124955d6dc0ba487","tid":418102,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"609c514adfe8adc53cc59dcbd4b137c3736fe1f9","tid":418102,"uid":39064,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:36:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/173047_28e940edbcd1e81f5699a326ddd7f708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F173047_28e940edbcd1e81f5699a326ddd7f708.jpg&h=25c6e183&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n老母係獌 個仔個猁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73978a0df2fec41d2b9ffc4836973db18e03632d","tid":418102,"uid":36045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"踢波受傷好正常啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個老母咩事"},{"pid":"fa944ef5302f5ad0ffddca1a8b570ebe4d569d0f","tid":418102,"uid":128863,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506674781_0d08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506674781_0d08.jpg&h=2e6db5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2013年8歲的男童在葵芳工廈內踢室內足球時，聲稱在從未受訓下被教練指派任守門員，結果在一次撲波